Introduction

Jjarimongttang (Korean: 짜리몽땅‬; The Shorties) was a South Korean girl group under CS Entertainment. They debuted on September 4, 2015 with the single "Dandelion". They presumably disbanded in 2016 due to inactivity on all of their platforms.
